<body>
	<div class="container navbar">
		<div class="navbar-inner">
			<a href = "#" class="brand">
				<img src="assets/pseudo-logo.png">
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<section class="hero-unit">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="span7">
					<div class="hero-unit-inner text-left">
						<h1> Your day, built around friends. </h1>
						<h4> Plan, edit, record, and share your day without ever touching a calendar. </h4>
						<h2><font color = "#ffa601" style="font-weight: 700"> Sign up</font> to become a beta tester. </h2>
						<form class="form-inline">
							<%= form_for @user, :method => :post do |f| %>
								<%= f.text_field :email, type: "email", class: "input-xlarge", placeholder: "Email"%>
								<%= f.submit "Get me started!", class: "btn btn-large" %>
							<% end %>
						</form>

						<small>
							Revyt does not disclose your personal information.
							<a href = "#privacyStatement" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> Privacy Statement </a>
						</small>

						<!-- Modal for Privacy Statement -->
						<div id="privacyStatement" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
							<div class="modal-header">
    							<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
								<h2 id = "myModalLabel">Privacy Statement</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="modal-body">
								<p><b>Revyt respects your privacy.</b></p>
								<p>Any personal information you provide to us including and similar to your name, address, telephone number and e-mail address will not be released, sold, or rented to any entities or individuals outside of Revyt.</p>

								<p><b>External Sites.</b></p>
								<p>Revyt is not responsible for the content of external internet sites. You are advised to read the privacy policy of external sites before disclosing any personal information.</p>

								<p><b>Cookies </b></p>
								<p>A "cookie" is a small data text file that is placed in your browser and allows Revyt to recognize you each time you visit this site. Cookies themselves do not contain any personal information, and Revyt does not use cookies to collect personal information. Cookies may also be used by 3rd party content providers such as newsfeeds.</p>

								<p><b>Remember The Risks Whenever You Use The Internet </b></p>
								<p>While we do our best to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee the security of any information that you transmit to Revyt and you are solely responsible for maintaining the secrecy of any passwords or other account information. In addition other Internet sites or services that may be accessible through Revyt have separate data and privacy practices independent of us, and therefore we disclaim any responsibility or liability for their policies or actions. </p>
								<p>Please contact those vendors and others directly if you have any questions about their privacy policies.</p>

								For any other information email <a href='mailto:support@revyt.com'>support@revyt.com</a>
							</div>
							<div class="modal-footer">
								<button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
							</div>
						</div> <!-- end modal -->

					</div> <!-- end hero-unit-inner -->
				</div>

				<div class="span5 move-up">
					<img src="assets/dummy-iphone.png" style="padding-left: 40px;" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section> <!-- end hero-unit -->

	<footer>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="span12 text-center">
					<a href="https://twitter.com/revyt1"><span class="footer-icon twitter-icon">&nbsp;</span></a>
					<a href="https://facebook.com/revyt"><span class="footer-icon facebook-icon">&nbsp;</span></a>
					<a href="mailto:support@revyt.com?subject=Service Request"><span class="footer-icon email-icon">&nbsp;</span></a>
			</div>
			<div class="row span12 text-center">
				<small> &copy; <a href="#">Revyt</a> 2013</small>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer> <!-- end footer -->

</body>
</html>